thinking of the riverbank, right?

60
00:04:07.720 --> 00:04:12.021
Totally different perception
of the same phrase.

61
00:04:12.021 --> 00:04:15.138
So the language we use
is really important.

62
00:04:15.138 --> 00:04:17.565
If we don't use the right language,

63
00:04:17.565 --> 00:04:21.806
we're gonna find ourselves with
quite significant problems.

64
00:04:21.806 --> 00:04:26.503
And we can help make that transition
not by just using clearer language but

65
00:04:26.503 --> 00:04:29.319
also by associating appropriate imagery.

66
00:04:29.319 --> 00:04:34.236
Just by you putting this image alongside
that text, I'm making it much clearer that

67
00:04:34.236 --> 00:04:37.297
I'm referring to the river
bank in that situation.

68
00:04:37.297 --> 00:04:40.878
Course I'd make it even clearer if I
said river bank rather than bank but

69
00:04:40.878 --> 00:04:41.779
you get the idea.

70
00:04:43.862 --> 00:04:48.796
Another way that we really need
to kind of prepare people and

71
00:04:48.796 --> 00:04:51.166
communicate that this is for

72
00:04:51.166 --> 00:04:55.523
them is through the choice
of imagery we use as well.

73
00:04:55.523 --> 00:04:59.034
And I gave that example earlier when
