00:05:06.320 --> 00:05:10.976
You need to be able to reflect back
the people that you're actually trying to

77
00:05:10.976 --> 00:05:15.488
reach in the interfaces that you're
creating in the imagery that you're

78
00:05:15.488 --> 00:05:16.590
choosing.

